{"tid":2102644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍南海軍演圖","createTime":"2020-07-10T15:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T00:32:50.000Z","uid":14918,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ab04c50d6e0a91afc8861152386406677571e76b","tid":2102644,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"USAF B-52 Conducts Maritime Integration Exercise With 2 US Navy CSG In The South China Sea<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.navalnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/USAF-B-52-Conducts-Maritime-Integration-Exercise-with-2-US-Navy-CSG-in-the-South-China-Sea-1-770x410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navalnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2FUSAF-B-52-Conducts-Maritime-Integration-Exercise-with-2-US-Navy-CSG-in-the-South-China-Sea-1-770x410.jpg&h=1e41e2a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">Aircraft from the Nimitz Carrier Strike Force and a B-52 Bomber from Barksdale Air Force base conduct integrated joint air operations in support of a free and open Indo-Pacific. The USS Nimitz (CVN 68) and USS Ronald Reagan (CVN 76) Carrier Strike Groups are conducting dual-carrier operations in the South China Sea as the Nimitz Carrier Strike Force. (U.S. Navy photo by Lt. Cmdr. Joseph Stephens)<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.navalnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/USAF-B-52-Conducts-Maritime-Integration-Exercise-with-2-US-Navy-CSG-in-the-South-China-Sea-3-1024x683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navalnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2FUSAF-B-52-Conducts-Maritime-Integration-Exercise-with-2-US-Navy-CSG-in-the-South-China-Sea-3-1024x683.jpg&h=ad3111ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">An F/A-18 Super Hornet attached to the &ldquo;Diamondbacks&rdquo; of Strike Fighter Squadron (VFA) 102 conducts air operations while flying with aircraft from the Nimitz Carrier Strike Force. The USS Nimitz (CVN 68) and USS Ronald Reagan (CVN 76) Carrier Strike Groups are conducting dual-carrier operations in the South China Sea as the Nimitz Carrier Strike Force. (U.S. Navy photo by Lt. Cmdr. Joseph Stephens)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.navalnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/USAF-B-52-Conducts-Maritime-Integration-Exercise-with-2-US-Navy-CSG-in-the-South-China-Sea-2-1024x683.jpg.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navalnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2FUSAF-B-52-Conducts-Maritime-Integration-Exercise-with-2-US-Navy-CSG-in-the-South-China-Sea-2-1024x683.jpg.webp&h=9a0fed91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.navalnews.com/naval-news/2020/07/usaf-b-52-conducts-maritime-integration-exercise-with-2-us-navy-csg-in-the-south-china-sea/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navalnews.com%2Fnaval-news%2F2020%2F07%2Fusaf-b-52-conducts-maritime-integration-exercise-with-2-us-navy-csg-in-the-south-china-sea%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=0544b33b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.navalnews.com/naval-news/2020/07/usaf-b-52-conducts-maritime-integration-exercise-with-2-us-navy-csg-in-the-south-china-sea/</a>"},{"pid":"7482e7bfef0c44636c9fb063cbe25881f3f618c2","tid":2102644,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d028dc5a50c12b58f3777c93a5d00ad7c998005","tid":2102644,"uid":12020,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:48:03.000Z","msg":"打未呀你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7183d0e7b91b38cc0e40b365ef45171d2e86cdd","tid":2102644,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"嚇鬼咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648d00436d6065285f68cc7f869b58fe7cbdaceb","tid":2102644,"uid":110672,"like":3,"dislike":